      "version": 92,
      "versionNonce": 1741908546,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1770735265930,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Best Practices",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Best Practices",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "B5q-YwuOuKbYujPGZsHzF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1400.4555992620494,
      "y": 231.406258572561,
      "width": 616,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "61IFNxQZenmb2sbk4Ngki",
      "index": "as",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 427042498,
      "version": 150,
      "versionNonce": 2083574274,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1770735265930,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Model Organization\n1. Define leaf models first- Models with no dependencies\n2. Build upward - Gradually compose more complex models\n3. Use clear naming - Make relationships obvious\nGroup related models - Keep models in logical modules",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Model Organization\n1. Define leaf models first- Models with no dependencies\n2. Build upward - Gradually compose more complex models\n3. Use clear naming - Make relationships obvious\nGroup related models - Keep models in logical modules",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "4rHxaNhHUHrjmZaKRvZF7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1403.2996901735053,
      "y": 387.52768281060924,
      "width": 693,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "61IFNxQZenmb2sbk4Ngki",
      "index": "at",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2124032066,
      "version": 178,
      "versionNonce": 940261826,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1770735265930,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Performance Considerations\n1. Deep nesting impacts performance - Keep reasonable depth\n2. Large lists of nested models - Consider pagination\n3. Circular references - Use carefully, can cause memory issues\n4. Lazy loading - Consider for expensive nested computations",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Performance Considerations\n1. Deep nesting impacts performance - Keep reasonable depth\n2. Large lists of nested models - Consider pagination\n3. Circular references - Use carefully, can cause memory issues\n4. Lazy loading - Consider for expensive nested computations",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BsUgpaUF8jzMsGjdjfYlM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1401.023420142424,
      "y": 569.0669623538015,
      "width": 781,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "61IFNxQZenmb2sbk4Ngki",
      "index": "au",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1137850142,
      "version": 97,
      "versionNonce": 914471298,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1770735265930,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Data Modeling Tips\n1. Model real-world relationships - Mirror your domain structure\n2. Use Optional appropriately - Not all relationships are required\n3. Consider Union types - For polymorphic relationships\n4. Validate business rules - Use model validators for cross-model logic",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Data Modeling Tips\n1. Model real-world relationships - Mirror your domain structure\n2. Use Optional appropriately - Not all relationships are required\n3. Consider Union types - For polymorphic relationships\n4. Validate business rules - Use model validators for cross-model logic",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
